            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hrmm. It feels so nice and warm today. *yawn* Hmm..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I think I ate too much for lunch."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "It's so nice and warm, and I'm so full... I'm getting slee‐zzz..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "So, as I was saying, I'd like to display several items from my treasured collection on the shop's shelves."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "But Mr. Owner, we don't have any shelves that we can spare for something as useless as that, you know?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "What!? \"Useless\"...?<CR>Come on, just a little room."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Even if it's an order from the owner, it's impossible."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "As the one who was entrusted with this shop, I need to give priority to selling... Oh!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "This girl is impossible. For a girl of marrying age to fall asleep in a place like this..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "She looks so peaceful and happy. Although, I guess Ayesha always is..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I wonder if I should wake her up..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Hey, Marietta, don't change the subject."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "First of all, my treasured items are not useless objects."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Even if they can't contribute to sales, I'm sure a customer with a good eye will eventually come, and..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "When exactly is \"eventually\"? You need to give me a detailed projection."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x24,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Ergh, that's..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x199,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Oh, Ayesha! Heya!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Zzz zzz..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x7e,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Heeey! Ayesha!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hrmm...hmhmhm, you can't. If you eat too much, you'll get fat, Bell..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x82,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Hmph, well aren't you having a rude dream!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x84,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "There was something I wanted to talk to you about, but I guess it can wait."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "My, my, sleeping in a place like this...?"
